body:
#### PR description:

In partial reply to https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/issues/49772. Update inputs for unit test `Miscellanea` of `Alignment/OfflineValidation` using the last library of phase-2 `TkAlZMuMu` ALCARECO files (from geometry D110, Tracker T35, which was spared at #49725).

#### PR validation:

`scram b runtests_Miscellanea` runs fine.

title: update unit test Miscellanea post integration of #49725
